text: D-216 was one of the most fun places I think in all of IITK. You were a great roommate, though would have been better if you stopped doing a few things. text: Yo Baketi! You are the perfect all-rounder if I have ever met one. It was amazing how well we were able to connect over the years. Knew each other in first year, but jyada kuchh interaction tab toh tha nahi, second year, kaafi masti kari Y18 orientation mein. Then thanks to Jagga and Avik making their group, we made our own duo, and what an epic duo. Numerous courses kiye saath mein, and aced so many assignments( in one course where we shouldn't have). Had so many joint study sessions in our rooms. I learnt lot from you in communication, interacting with people, understanding others, and so many other people skills, I will always be grateful for that. Baaki acads ke alawa bhi kaafi masti kari from chess matches, marvel and House MD discussions, past experience sharing and whatnot.  Best of luck future CEO. Touch mein toh rehna hi hai. 3 Marvel shows hai pending mein hai, ab jaldi khatam kar.
author: Devansh  Shringi

text:
Yo Yasharth,

Really enjoyed tutoring students with you in ESC101 as well. Good luck so you reach the heights without much stress. Hope to stay in contact.
